Every time I open KSP, my saves don't show.

I've checked the save file, and all my saves are there, but when I run KSP and click "Resume Save" It shows a blank GUI.

I believe DarkMultiPlayer caused the problem, and so I deleted it and every other mod, but it still doesn't show the saves.

 

Any idea on how to fix this?
